data.description: Price Reduction! Sellers are motivated, offering $5,000 towards buyers closing costs! Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Minneola! This meticulously maintained 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. You will find yourself right at home from the moment you open the door and are greeted by the open floorplan. The entire home is warm and welcoming, flowing seamlessly with luxury engineered wood flooring throughout the primary living space. With one of the largest lots in the neighborhood you will enjoy relaxing in your beautifully fenced back yard. Plus, the privacy bonus of having no direct rear neighbors! Every corner has been thoughtfully designed and cared for. With something for everyone, this property is poised to be your family's haven. Walking distance to highly rated schools and the Minneola athletic complex. Publix and Starbucks are only 1 mile away! Don't miss the chance to call this your new home, request a showing today!
